{"word":"ἀμφιχέω","slug":"ἀμφιχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n6138\" key=\"a)mfixe/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀμφιχέω</orth>, <sense id=\"n6138.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pour around, pour</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">spread over,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφὶ δ᾽ ἄρ᾽ ἑρμῖσιν χέε</foreign> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δέσματα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:278\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.278</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n6138.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> mostly <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be poured</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shed around,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πάρος κόνιν ἀμφιχυθῆναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:764\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.764</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: c. acc., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θείη δέ μιν ἀμφέχυτ᾽ ὀμφή</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.41</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν ἄχος ἀμφεχύθη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:716\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.716</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀμφιχυθὲν γῆρας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0255.tlg001:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Mimn.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφὶ δὲ σποδὸν κάρᾳ κεχύμεθα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">we have</tr_> ashes <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">poured over</tr_> our head, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg008.perseus-grc1:826\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Supp.\">Supp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">826</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n6138.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of persons, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">embrace,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀμφιχυθεὶς πατέρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:214\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.214</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:498\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.498</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}